## 🧪 Testing Strategy

### Test-First Development

```typescript
// 1. Write the test
describe('Voice Agent', () => {
  it('should create agent with user isolation', async () => {
    const agent = await createVoiceAgent({ name: 'Test' });
    expect(agent.userId).toBe(mockUser.id);
  });
});

// 2. Then implement
export async function createVoiceAgent(data) {
  const user = await currentUser();
  if (!user) throw new Error('Unauthorized');
  // Implementation
}
```

### Database Testing Pattern

Use transactions for safe testing:

```typescript
await db.transaction(async (tx) => {
  // Test your database operations
  const result = await createRecord(data, tx);

  // Verify the result
  expect(result).toBeDefined();

  // Transaction rolls back automatically
  throw new Error('Rollback');
});
```

